description:
In this video I'm showcasing and ranking 100 different tracks I've made in various TrackMania games over the years. The video was originally supposed to come out in March 2017, but several technical challenges prevented my from making the video back then (mainly related to very hard disk space).

This video expands on the original idea tough, since I originally only wanted to showcase TMNF and TMUF tracks, this video will also showcase stuff I've made in TrackMania² games as well as the new TrackMania game.
